            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PS4</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>The "Doppelganger" launches this summer.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Arc System Works [1,340 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/arc-system-works">Arc System Works</a> and developer <a title="Companies > French-Bread [139 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/french-bread">French-Bread</a> have <a href="https://twitter.com/inbirthPR/status/2050168937997041860" target="_blank">announced</a> <em><a title="Games > Under Night In-Birth II Sys:Celes [14 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/under-night-in-birth-ii-sysceles">Under Night In-Birth II Sys:Celes</a></em> downloadable content character Zohar. She will launch this summer. <span id="more-1045355"></span></p><p>“Claws encroaching unseen, the ‘Doppelganger’ finally joins as the [fourth downloadable content] fighter in summer 2026,” reads the announcement. “Battle style and ability details are scheduled to be revealed at a later date. Stay tuned!”</p><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/UNIB2-DLC_05-01-26_002.jpg"></a></figure><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/UNIB2-DLC_05-01-26_003.jpg"></a></figure><p><em>Under Night In-Birth II Sys:Celes</em> is available now for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,737 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2076010/UNDER_NIGHT_INBIRTH_II_SysCeles/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>.</p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/05/under-night-in-birth-ii-sysceles-dlc-character-zohar-announced]]></content:encoded>
